            "body": "Sure, makes sense. Currently the output is collected in `s_output` https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/0d16260b49d4bb702027c998bbcf00c4ea94089f/runtime/lua/vim/health.lua#L264 and printed in one final \"batch\". That could instead be appended to the checkhealth buffer incrementally.",
